description:
&lt;p&gt;Circle Health is a company that runs hospitals and health services in the UK.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Circle Bath (Private Healthcare Provider) is growing and we have an exciting opportunity for Registered Nurses to join our Bank Register. We first opened our doors in March 2010. Designed by renowned architect Sir Norman Foster, our award-winning private hospital offers both inpatient and outpatient care in a unique setting overlooking the Somerset countryside. Circle Bath was a pioneer in developing hospitals that feel more like a hotel. In 2014, it was ranked among the highest-scoring hospitals for patient-reported outcomes in hip and knee surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role &amp; Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to for a Registered Nurse to join our team in our Inpatient Unit, at the Circle Hospital in Bath. Our hospital is only 10 years old and is a stylish, modern independent hospital offering elective surgical procedures. We are looking for a Registered Nurse who is compassionate, enthusiastic, highly motivated and looking for a challenge. You must possess excellent communication skills, be committed to delivering high standards of care and in return we will offer you support, professional development and a stylish, modern environment to work within.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Person Specification:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NMC registration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrable record of CPD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of current issues in professional practice with particular relevance to the Unit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Surgical ward nursing experience is desirable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free Parking on site&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhanced Pay rates for unsociable hours for weekends and evenings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health and Well Being programme which includes free fruit, massages and fitness sessions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Discounted food from the Atrium Café&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
